# 從頭再嚟
(pos: 動詞短語 / 成語)
<explanation>
yue: 將之前做過嘅嘢全部推翻，由最初嗰一步重新開始做（量詞：次）
eng: to start all over again; to begin from scratch
<eg>
yue: 個蛋糕燒焦咗，我哋要從頭再嚟做過。 (go3 daai6 gou1 siu1 giu1 zo2, ngo5 dei6 jiu6 waak6 caang4 zoi6 lai4 zou6 gwo3.)
eng: The cake burnt, so we have to start all over again.

<eg>
yue: 雖然今次輸咗，但係我哋唔使灰心，可以從頭再嚟。 (sui1 jin4 gam1 sing1 syu1 zo2, daan6 hai6 ngo5 dei6 m4 sai6 fai1 sam1, ho2 ji5 caang4 zoi6 lai4.)
eng: Although we lost this time, we shouldn't be discouraged; we can start all over again. [end of text]


